---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="bg-surface py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Tilläggstjänster till din Städning
      </h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">
        Komplettera med fönsterputsning eller strykning i Stockholm. Alltid med
        50% RUT-avdrag.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-3xl grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <a
        class="bg-surface-container-low hover:bg-surface-container group flex items-center gap-6 rounded-xl p-6 transition-colors"
        href="/services/windows-cleaning"
      >
        <div
          class="bg-primary-fixed flex h-14 w-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
        >
          <Icon name="material-symbols:window" class="text-primary size-6" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4
            class="group-hover:text-primary mb-1 text-lg font-bold transition-colors"
          >
            Professionell Fönsterputsning
          </h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
            Skinande rena fönster utan ränder för både hus och lägenheter.
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a
        class="bg-surface-container-low hover:bg-surface-container group flex items-center gap-6 rounded-xl p-6 transition-colors"
        href="/services/iron-service"
      >
        <div
          class="bg-primary-fixed flex h-14 w-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
        >
          <Icon name="material-symbols:iron" class="text-primary size-7" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4
            class="group-hover:text-primary mb-1 text-lg font-bold transition-colors"
          >
            Strykning & Klädvård
          </h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
            Spara tid i vardagen. Vi stryker dina kläder bekvämt i ditt hem.
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
